mochi Toya 开玩笑说其他主播患有多动症">Nijisanji YouTuber Kenmochi Toya 开玩笑说其他主播患有多动症</a></p><cite>动漫新闻网</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“No.2（暂定）”</em> /虚拟元宇宙VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="5VluoMrqud"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/nijisanji-vtuber-kenmochi-toya-adhd-comment-is-reported-critically/">NIJISANJI VTuber Kenmochi Toya 的“多动症评论”受到批评</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“NIJISANJI VTuber Kenmochi Toya 的“多动症评论”受到批评” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/nijisanji-vtuber-kenmochi-toya-adhd-comment-is-reported-critically/embed/#?secret=GvqXcD1wVt#?secret=5VluoMrqud" data-secret="5VluoMrqud" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/kadokawa-affiliated-media-critically-reported-on-nijisanji-vtuber-kenmochi-toya-adhd-comment/">角川系海外媒体的</a>帖子首次刊登于<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a> 。; https://p2y.jp/kadokawa-affiliated-media-riticly-reported-on-nijisanji-vtuber-kenmochi-toya-adhd-comment/feed/ 0 99987
